This is the hardare design for a circuirt board that has 12 0.5 watt LEDs. It's designed to run off of a nominal 48 VDC, and has a PWM line that can be use to control the brightness.

The design was made in Kicad. Changes, updates, and suggestions are appreciated.

You can find more information here:
http://smg.tophi.net/content/led-tile

